The utility functions are implemented with an assumption of 16 bit PCM audio format.

16-bit Mono   : 8bit-LSB+ 8bit-MSB  |  8bit-LSB+8bit-MSB
	      	  16bit-Sample-1    |    16bit-Sample-2

16-bit Stereo : Left Channel 	    |  Right Channel
		8bit-LSB+8bit-MSB   |  8bit-LSB+8bit-MSB
	      	16bit-Sample-1      |  16bit-Sample-2  
